extends layout

block content
	//- This is just a sample view rendered by our index controller.
	h1 Here are the rides you requested:

	//- Placeholder ride table
	table.table.table-striped.table-hover.hide
		thead
		tr
			th Name
			th Style
			th Time
			th Distance
			th Speed
			th Elevation
			th Description
		tbody
		tr.success
			td.nme
			a.name.rain(href='#', data-id='00') Rain, Mud, sand, and good times
			td.style(data-id='RS') Road Speed
			td.time(data-id='90m') 1:27:51
			td.dist(data-id='25mi') 20.3 mi
			td.spd(data-id='15') 12.5 mi/h
			td.el(data-id='1500ft') 1,145 ft
			td.desc(data-id='zz')
			| This ride is a great challenge of effort. Some undulation pushing you for more speed, more effort, and testing your pain threshold!




	//- Give users a link to log out of their account
	p: a(href="/auth/logout") Log out